snippet.textDisplay:
Disgraceful.  Australia, hang your head in shame.  

He met the visa requirements and travelled accordingly. Then he was arrested on entry and put in a hotel that he was 'free to leave' from.  Only if he did he would have been deported.

He wasn't a threat to public health so this decision can only be for political reasons and to make a point to force more people to get the jab.

I won't watch the Australian Open and the winner this year will forever have their title tainted.

Australia has lost its collective reasoning.  Hitler and Stalin would be very proud of what it has achieved in this pandemic.
